ng\ntwo models of set theory, one an outer (modal) model, the other an inner,\ngeneralized metric model with an information minimization principle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 29 Jul 2018 18:36:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 27 Apr 2019 20:51:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 11 May 2019 12:26:57 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 15 Jun 2019 10:27:17 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sun, 12 Jan 2020 17:59:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-14"}
