h the fundamental, scheme-independent Generalized Crewther\nrelations which connect observables, such as deep inelastic neutrino-nucleon\nscattering, to hadronic $e^+e^-$ annihilation. Thus, by using the combination\nof the PMC series and the Pad\\'e method, the predictive power of pQCD theory\ncan be greatly improved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Jul 2018 02:24:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Jan 2019 01:29:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-27"}
