 and compared to a baseline strategy using an off-the-shelf clustering\napproach. We illustrate the importance of the persistence atlas in a variety of\nreal-life datasets, where clear trends in feature layouts are identified and\nanalyzed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Jul 2018 07:46:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-31"}
